snippet.title: Nintendo Nightmare DX Deluxe F3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Post-Launch trailer first seen during Kaze Emanuar's F3 Conference, held at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0htUp3MoBjA

Link to game: https://fazana.itch.io/910-nightmare-dx

Credits to Sikowny for doing the trailer voiceover (except for that one line about 10 years, that was meeeeee)
